<title>USA: TABLE-Circuit City July same-store sales down.</title>
<headline>TABLE-Circuit City July same-store sales down.</headline>
<dateline>RICHMOND, Va. 1997-08-06</dateline>
<text>
<p>Percent change</p>
<p>		    1997	 1996	     Total     Same-Store</p>
<p>Month	     $581.4     $539.8	  +8	   -5</p>
<p>NOTE: Figures in millions except percentage.</p>
<p>Month is 31 days ended July 31.</p>
<p>The results in the table are for the Circuit City Group.</p>
<p>The company also reported an 11 percent total sales increase in July of $647.7 million, up from $581.3 million, for Circuit City Stores Inc.</p>
<p>Total sales in July for the CarMax Group were $66.3 million, a total increase of 60 percent over the $41.5 million in sales in 1996 and a 10 percent increase in comparable store sales.</p>
